and I have to look for jobs again.

601
00:22:01,370 --> 00:22:02,260
You

602
00:22:03,500 --> 00:22:04,500
work very hard

603
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:05,770
but you don't get paid a lot.

604
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:08,570
Why are you so adamant

605
00:22:08,570 --> 00:22:09,740
about doing things the right way?

606
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,530
My mother-in-law said the same thing too.

607
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:12,900
That I'm adamant

608
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:14,020
and headstrong.

609
00:22:15,050 --> 00:22:15,900
But I don't think

610
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:16,980
it's a bad thing.

611
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:18,660
We should know

612
00:22:18,660 --> 00:22:19,500
what's right and what's wrong.

613
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,220
Don't you think?

614
00:22:21,460 --> 00:22:22,420
So

615
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:24,610
I treat you to this meal

616
00:22:24,770 --> 00:22:26,260
to thank you.

617
00:22:28,050 --> 00:22:28,980
For what?

618
00:22:30,980 --> 00:22:31,980
I kept thinking,

619
00:22:33,660 --> 00:22:35,090
if you weren't there to keep an eye on me,

620
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,180
to question me,

621
00:22:36,530 --> 00:22:37,570
and to ask for justifications,

622
00:22:37,810 --> 00:22:39,260
or if I knew about this

623
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:41,370
in a more private setting,

624
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:43,570
would I have acquiesced in their decision?

625
00:22:44,850 --> 00:22:45,530
After all, this case

626
00:22:45,530 --> 00:22:46,090
would bring in

627
00:22:46,090 --> 00:22:47,420
a lot of money to the firm.

628
00:22:47,530 --> 00:22:48,810
And we need money.

629
00:22:50,370 --> 00:22:51,740
So you're thanking me for this?

630
00:22:53,090 --> 00:22:54,330
Would you have condoned it then?

631
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:00,610
I don't know.

632
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:02,420
Do you think I'd have done it?

633
00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:04,020
No.

634
00:23:05,660 --> 00:23:07,130
Starting your own business

635
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,530
is as difficult as it is.

636
00:23:09,180 --> 00:23:10,370
But you remain

637
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,090
a man of integrity,

638
00:23:12,460 --> 00:23:13,330
a man of his word,

639
00:23:13,330 --> 00:23:14,900
and a man who's hardworking.

640
00:23:14,980 --> 00:23:15,980
You're trustworthy

641
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:17,020
and you can give people a sense of security.

642
00:23:17,770 --> 00:23:19,460
I don't think you will do such a thing.

643
00:23:20,090 --> 00:23:20,940
Xingfu,

644
00:23:23,570 --> 00:23:24,420
you're more resilient than me.

645
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:25,900
You're an amazing person.

646
00:23:28,050 --> 00:23:29,850
Don't you make fun of me.

647
00:23:30,130 --> 00:23:31,130
If I'm amazing,

648
00:23:31,130 --> 00:23:31,940
then everyone else

649
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,460
will be spectacular then.

650
00:23:34,220 --> 00:23:35,020
Let's eat.

651
00:23:44,770 --> 00:23:45,460
Hello, Xingyun.

652
00:23:45,850 --> 00:23:46,570
What's the matter?

653
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:47,570
Senior.

654
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:48,610
Did Mr. Liu

655
00:23:48,610 --> 00:23:50,220
[Archive]
go to your firm?

656
00:23:50,570 --> 00:23:51,050
Yes.

657
00:23:51,370 --> 00:23:52,260
How did you know?

658
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:56,050
He came to Yidao today

659
00:23:56,290 --> 00:23:57,940
and has signed the contract.

660
00:23:58,610 --> 00:23:59,980
I thought about it

661
00:24:00,220 --> 00:24:00,980
and I felt the need

662
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:02,610
to inform you.

663
00:24:03,090 --> 00:24:04,700
When Mr. Liu came today,

664
00:24:04,700 --> 00:24:05,500
he left

665
00:24:05,500 --> 00:24:07,330
scathing remarks about your firm.

666
00:24:09,370 --> 00:24:10,180
I see.

667
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:12,460
It's just a reminder.

668
00:24:12,980 --> 00:24:14,660
It's not good to get on a client's bad side.

669
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:15,610
I know.

670
00:24:15,850 --> 00:24:16,530
Thank you.

671
00:24:18,020 --> 00:24:19,420
I'm eating with your sister.

672
00:24:19,530 --> 00:24:20,660
Do you want to talk to her?

673
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:22,180
No, thanks.

674
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:23,610
This is not a convenient time.

675
00:24:23,610 --> 00:24:24,980
We can have a chat when we meet.

676
00:24:25,370 --> 00:24:26,130
Sure. See you.

677
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:27,050
All right. Bye.

678
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:31,900
Xingyun told me

679
00:24:32,090 --> 00:24:33,330
that Mr. Liu's case would no longer

680
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:34,050
be handled by us.

681
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:35,460
And it's their firm

682
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:38,220
that took over.

683
00:24:38,610 --> 00:24:39,130
What?

684
00:24:41,090 --> 00:24:41,980
Why?

685
00:24:43,530 --> 00:24:44,220
I don't know.

686
00:24:45,050 --> 00:24:46,290
Apparently, Mr. Liu

687
00:24:46,940 --> 00:24:48,180
wasn't very happy with the meeting.

688
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:51,090
I didn't notice.

689
00:24:52,610 --> 00:24:53,570
He seemed very happy

690
00:24:53,570 --> 00:24:54,700
when he left.

691
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:57,260
He even said he would bring more documents.

692
00:24:58,290 --> 00:24:59,370
What a sly fox.

693
00:25:01,610 --> 00:25:02,740
It's okay. It's all in the past now.

694
00:25:02,810 --> 00:25:03,850
Forget it. Just eat.

695
00:25:04,290 --> 00:25:04,770
Here.

696
00:25:07,130 --> 00:25:07,900
This soup is good.

697
00:25:14,530 --> 00:25:15,900
Why are you on the bed?

698
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:18,020
Don't you have a night shift?

699
00:25:19,740 --> 00:25:20,940
You came back late.

700
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:23,370
I sent you a message

701
00:25:23,370 --> 00:25:24,290
and said I'd be late.

702
00:25:24,330 --> 00:25:25,500
Guan Tao treated me to a meal.

703
00:25:26,290 --> 00:25:27,290
And then we went back

704
00:25:27,290 --> 00:25:28,420
to do some paperwork.

705
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:29,660
He treated you to a meal?

706
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:31,700
Why?

707
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,220
Just to talk about some business.

708
00:25:35,610 --> 00:25:36,700
You haven't had dinner yet, right?

709
00:25:37,050 --> 00:25:38,090
Let me cook some noodles for you.

710
00:25:39,660 --> 00:25:40,570
Get up now.

711
00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:55,020
Why would Guan Tao treat you to a meal?

712
00:25:56,130 --> 00:25:57,530
It's about a case.

713
00:25:57,900 --> 00:25:59,330
A businessman wanted us

714
00:25:59,330 --> 00:26:00,570
to handle a case

715
00:26:00,810 --> 00:26:02,370
but then something happened

716
00:26:02,530 --> 00:26:03,700
and everything went sour.

717
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:06,130
And he treated you to a meal for that?

718
00:26:06,460 --> 00:26:07,260
Is he crazy?

719
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:11,660
You won't understand anyway.

720
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:13,740
Guan Tao just said

721
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:14,700
that thanks to me,

722
00:26:14,700 --> 00:26:15,740
he avoided doing something wrong.

723
00:26:17,660 --> 00:26:18,660
You're just

724
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:19,900
a janitor.

725
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:21,330
What did you do to help him

726
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:23,290
to deserve a free meal?

727
00:26:24,330 --> 00:26:25,330
You...

728
00:26:26,610 --> 00:26:28,370
What's wrong with me being a janitor?

729
00:26:29,500 --> 00:26:30,500
Not only did I clean,

730
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:32,090
but I did a lot of other stuff too.

731
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:34,940
The three young lawyers there

732
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:36,020
don't have an assistant.

733
00:26:36,530 --> 00:26:37,700
I helped them

734
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:38,980
with many things as well.

735
00:26:40,090 --> 00:26:41,770
Don't you underestimate me.

736
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:44,460
I'm an important member of the firm now.

737
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:46,260
And maybe one day,

738
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:47,260
I'll become a receptionist.

739
00:26:47,260 --> 00:26:48,460
And you'll be shocked.

740
00:26:49,850 --> 00:26:51,370
You make yourself sound so capable.

741
00:26:52,570 --> 00:26:54,020
You might think that you are important to them.

742
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:56,370
But they are probably thinking otherwise.

743
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,980
I don't care what people think of me.

744
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:00,850
I just have to do my duty.

745
00:27:02,610 --> 00:27:03,610
I even wondered

746
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,370
when we could head back to the village.

747
00:27:05,370 --> 00:27:06,330
Then I can ask around

748
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:08,130
and recommend our law firm

749
00:27:08,130 --> 00:27:09,610
to those who need a lawyer.

750
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:13,530
You're even helping them

751
00:27:14,850 --> 00:27:15,850
to look for more clients.

752
00:27:16,810 --> 00:27:18,290
Will they pay you more?

753
00:27:19,330 --> 00:27:21,050
You cannot think it that way.

754
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,180
If the firm declares bankruptcy,

755
00:27:23,180 --> 00:27:24,610
I'll lose my job too.

756
00:27:27,220 --> 00:27:28,740
I just think it's odd

757
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:32,770
that he treated you to a meal.

758
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:35,610
I'll invite you next time.

759
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,500
Then it won't be odd, right?

760
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:44,740
For this month,

761
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:46,020
the rent is 18,000 yuan.

762
00:27:48,090 --> 00:27:49,460
The utility bill

763
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:51,740
is 4,200 yuan

764
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:53,020
in all.

765
00:27:53,940 --> 00:27:55,900
The administrative expenditure

766
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,610
is 5,600...

767
00:27:57,770 --> 00:27:58,810
I'll round it up to 5,700 yuan.

768
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:02,610
Xingfu's salary

769
00:28:03,130 --> 00:28:04,610
is 1,500 yuan.

770
00:28:04,610 --> 00:28:05,420
[Utility, Administrative Expenditure, Salary]

771
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:06,020
How much is it in total?

772
00:28:08,850 --> 00:28:09,900
29,400 yuan.

773
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,530
We only had

774
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:12,810
a few small cases this month.

775
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:13,850
We'd be considered lucky

776
00:28:13,850 --> 00:28:15,420
if we could earn 20,000 yuan.

777
00:28:16,050 --> 00:28:16,500
See?

778
00:28:16,660 --> 00:28:18,180
Another month in deficit.

779
00:28:24,850 --> 00:28:26,090
The beginning is the toughest.

780
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:27,260
Oh,

781
00:28:27,370 --> 00:28:28,610
after Mr. Liu

782
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:29,850
left,

783
00:28:30,130 --> 00:28:31,220
he never came back.

784
00:28:31,530 --> 00:28:32,180
I called him

785
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:33,260
and he never gave me a clear answer.

786
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:34,700
Did something happen?

787
00:28:35,290 --> 00:28:36,130
His case

788
00:28:36,130 --> 00:28:37,500
is now handled by Yidao.

789
00:28:39,050 --> 00:28:40,180
We need to find a way

790
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:41,420
to look for new cases.

791
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:43,020
I never knew looking for clients

792
00:28:43,020 --> 00:28:44,530
was this difficult.

793
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:46,530
Come in.

794
00:28:48,530 --> 00:28:49,180
Mr. Guan.

795
00:28:51,570 --> 00:28:52,050
Hi.

796
00:28:52,500 --> 00:28:52,980
Madam,

797
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,290
this is Mr. Guan.

798
00:28:54,610 --> 00:28:55,810
He represented my family

799
00:28:55,810 --> 00:28:57,180
in the land dispute case.

800
00:28:57,740 --> 00:28:58,330
Mr. Guan.

801
00:28:58,330 --> 00:28:59,420
-Hi.
-Hi, I'm Guan Tao.

802
00:29:00,570 --> 00:29:01,330
Please have a seat.

803
00:29:03,290 --> 00:29:03,770
Okay.

804
00:29:04,370 --> 00:29:04,810
Take a seat.

805
00:29:07,610 --> 00:29:08,500
Please sit here.

806
00:29:08,810 --> 00:29:09,290
Xingfu.

807
00:29:09,570 --> 00:29:10,090
Serve some water.

808
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:12,810
I'm not thirsty.

809
00:29:13,180 --> 00:29:14,260
Don't go.

810
00:29:14,260 --> 00:29:15,370
Stay here.

811
00:29:15,700 --> 00:29:16,530
I...

812
00:29:17,370 --> 00:29:18,530
I'll sit here then.

813
00:29:25,050 --> 00:29:26,530
Have you encountered any problems?

814
00:29:29,130 --> 00:29:30,570
Are you really from Wan Village?

815
00:29:31,530 --> 00:29:33,940
Well, I couldn't tell at all.

816
00:29:34,180 --> 00:29:35,610
I'm just in my work uniform. That's all.

817
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:37,220
I just started

818
00:29:37,290 --> 00:29:38,290
working here.

819
00:29:39,460 --> 00:29:39,900
Madam,

820
00:29:40,050 --> 00:29:40,980
can you tell us

821
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:42,900
more about your problem?

822
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:44,260
Mr. Guan is here.

823
00:29:47,900 --> 00:29:49,330
You know, Shiqiao Village...

824
00:29:51,530 --> 00:29:52,020
It's just

825
00:29:52,130 --> 00:29:53,050
when I mention it,

826
00:29:53,610 --> 00:29:55,130
I get overwhelmed.

827
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:55,940
Calm down.

828
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:56,980
There's no outsider here.

829
00:29:57,740 --> 00:29:58,850
Just tell me.

830
00:30:00,740 --> 00:30:02,530
We plant apples there.

831
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:04,900
A few years ago, thanks to good sales,

832
00:30:05,130 --> 00:30:06,370
a company came

833
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:08,810
to sign a bought deal.

834
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,020
They offered 1.5 yuan for one jin of apples

835
00:30:10,020 --> 00:30:11,180
and they wanted all our produce.

836
00:30:11,570 --> 00:30:12,460
We thought

837
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:13,900
even though it was lower

838
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:15,940
than the market price,

839
00:30:16,180 --> 00:30:18,020
it saves us the hassle

840
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,130
and the risk.

841
00:30:19,740 --> 00:30:20,570
So everyone

842
00:30:20,570 --> 00:30:21,530
in the village

843
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:22,660
converted their farmlands

844
00:30:22,660 --> 00:30:24,290
into orchards.

845
00:30:24,770 --> 00:30:25,940
Now that the apple trees have matured

846
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,130
and the apples are ripe,

847
00:30:27,370 --> 00:30:29,330
everyone has their land decked
with heaps of apples.

848
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:30,180
Not long ago,

849
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:31,290
they told us

850
00:30:31,420 --> 00:30:32,940
apples weren't in high demand anymore

851
00:30:33,130 --> 00:30:34,700
so they decreased the price

852
00:30:34,850 --> 00:30:35,940
to 1.2 yuan per jin.

853
00:30:36,610 --> 00:30:37,500
We thought to ourselves

854
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,420
that there were just

855
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,980
too many apples to be sold by ourselves.

856
00:30:40,050 --> 00:30:41,090
So we agreed to it.

857
00:30:41,260 --> 00:30:41,940
But then

858
00:30:41,940 --> 00:30:43,260
they never came.

859
00:30:43,530 --> 00:30:44,530
We were so desperate

860
00:30:44,530 --> 00:30:45,420
and we went to them.

861
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,940
Then they told us

862
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:48,610
that apples were unsalable now

863
00:30:48,770 --> 00:30:49,850
so they would withdraw from the deal.

864
00:30:50,180 --> 00:30:50,940
We were at our wit's end

865
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,370
so we turned

866
00:30:52,570 --> 00:30:54,290
to our previous clients

867
00:30:54,570 --> 00:30:56,220
but they wouldn't buy from us again.

868
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:58,090
They had already bought enough apples.

869
00:31:00,260 --> 00:31:01,770
It's so unfair.

870
00:31:02,090 --> 00:31:03,660
A year of hard work

871
00:31:05,330 --> 00:31:07,050
is now rotting

872
00:31:07,050 --> 00:31:08,770
at our home.

873
00:31:11,370 --> 00:31:13,050
They violated the agreement.

874
00:31:13,610 --> 00:31:14,180
Madam,

875
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:15,850
did you guys sign a contract?

876
00:31:16,290 --> 00:31:16,850
Yes, we did.

877
00:31:16,850 --> 00:31:17,940
Of course, we did.

878
00:31:18,050 --> 00:31:19,660
But they refuse to acknowledge it.

879
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,700
Why is our life

880
00:31:22,700 --> 00:31:24,050
so tough?

881
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:25,900
Right.

882
00:31:26,180 --> 00:31:28,370
I sympathize with you.

883
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:29,900
But we have Mr. Guan here.

884
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:31,290
He'll help us.

885
00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:35,050
I'm so worried.

886
00:31:35,330 --> 00:31:36,420
One year of hard work

887
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:38,420
is rotting at home.

888
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:42,020
My baby still needs to be breastfed.

889
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:43,290
Due to my anxiety,

890
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:44,660
I stopped lactating.

891
00:31:45,370 --> 00:31:46,850
Now that I cannot breastfeed my baby,

892
00:31:47,020 --> 00:31:48,570
he cries every day.

893
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:51,370
It pains me to see it.

894
00:31:52,050 --> 00:31:52,940
Wipe your tears, madam.

895
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,050
Why are they crying?

896
00:32:11,940 --> 00:32:12,810
I know, right?

897
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:14,330
Why...

898
00:32:14,330 --> 00:32:15,740
Why are they both crying?

899
00:32:17,940 --> 00:32:19,050
You idiot.

900
00:32:20,610 --> 00:32:21,980
This is Xingfu's strategy

901
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:25,130
to bond with the client.

902
00:32:26,610 --> 00:32:27,290
A strategy, you say?

903
00:32:28,770 --> 00:32:30,050
Maybe you can pull it off in front of me

904
00:32:30,050 --> 00:32:30,530
next time.

905
00:32:32,570 --> 00:32:33,420
Being with you here

906
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,020
and ranting to you

907
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:36,980
has made me feel better.

908
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:41,330
Actually, my family

909
00:32:41,980 --> 00:32:43,650
was against my signing the contract

910
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:45,740
with the company.

911
00:32:46,220 --> 00:32:47,410
But I insisted

912
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:50,610
that a sales and purchase agreement

913
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:51,940
with a large company like that

914
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:53,810
would be very reliable.

915
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,330
That's why I signed it.

916
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:56,810
Now that this has happened,

917
00:32:57,650 --> 00:32:59,570
my family resents me.

918
00:33:01,650 --> 00:33:03,300
I don't have a space to vent.

919
00:33:05,060 --> 00:33:06,940
Do you think I can be helped?

920
00:33:07,170 --> 00:33:07,940
Of course.

921
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:09,300
There must be a way.

922
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:10,570
You

923
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:11,570
came here

924
00:33:12,020 --> 00:33:13,330
to look for a solution, didn't you?

925
00:33:13,850 --> 00:33:14,740
Like

926
00:33:14,810 --> 00:33:15,570
talking

927
00:33:15,890 --> 00:33:17,020
to the lawyers?

928
00:33:17,850 --> 00:33:18,540
Yes.

929
00:33:19,610 --> 00:33:21,060
But I don't know anything.

930
00:33:21,810 --> 00:33:23,460
That's precisely

931
00:33:23,540 --> 00:33:24,540
why lawyers represent us

932
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:25,810
in a legal case.

933
00:33:26,610 --> 00:33:27,220
Madam,

934
00:33:27,410 --> 00:33:28,300
if you trust me,

935
00:33:28,330 --> 00:33:29,570
you should trust Mr. Guan too.

936
00:33:29,890 --> 00:33:31,220
He'll definitely help us.

937
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:36,370
All right.

938
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,370
If you say so,

939
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:39,570
I believe you.

940
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:42,980
But I don't have a lot of money.

941
00:33:48,940 --> 00:33:50,060
Don't worry

942
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:51,410
about the money.

943
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:53,810
We can discuss it

944
00:33:53,810 --> 00:33:54,940
once the case

945
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,780
is settled.

946
00:33:58,130 --> 00:33:58,780
But now,

947
00:33:58,780 --> 00:34:00,220
I want you to give me

948
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:02,090
the name of the company you signed

949
00:34:02,090 --> 00:34:02,650
the contract with

950
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:04,020
and the content

951
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:04,890
of the agreement.

952
00:34:07,130 --> 00:34:08,090
Here, madam.

953
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,130
See you.

954
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:15,290
Take care.

955
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:17,940
Xingfu.

956
00:34:18,290 --> 00:34:19,290
I'm so glad

957
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:20,730
that I found you.

958
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:21,770
I'll let them

959
00:34:21,770 --> 00:34:22,940
handle this case then.

960
00:34:23,340 --> 00:34:24,420
We're from the same region.

961
00:34:24,540 --> 00:34:26,290
Keep an eye on my case, will you?

962
00:34:26,770 --> 00:34:27,500
Don't worry.

963
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:28,290
They

964
00:34:28,290 --> 00:34:29,610
are very hardworking.

965
00:34:29,610 --> 00:34:30,980
I'm sure they'll handle it very well
without any supervision.

966
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:32,020
All right.

967
00:34:32,650 --> 00:34:33,690
I'll leave then.

968
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:35,210
If you ever head back,

969
00:34:35,340 --> 00:34:36,290
do take a detour

970
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:37,770
and drop by my place.

971
00:34:37,770 --> 00:34:38,570
Of course.

972
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:40,540
Please keep an eye on my case.

973
00:34:40,730 --> 00:34:41,420
Have a safe trip.

974
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:41,860
Okay.

975
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:42,650
Bye.

976
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:43,650
Bye.

977
00:34:49,570 --> 00:34:50,250
Mr. Guan.

978
00:34:51,090 --> 00:34:52,130
How much is this case worth?

979
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:57,650
Not a lot.

980
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:02,570
But it's okay.

981
00:35:03,060 --> 00:35:04,210
It's not a lot

982
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:06,460
but it's for the greater good.

983
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:07,730
Can't...

984
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:09,690
Can't win an argument against you then.

985
00:35:11,090 --> 00:35:12,290
But you save money

986
00:35:12,290 --> 00:35:13,290
little by little.

987
00:35:14,340 --> 00:35:15,500
I earn 1,500 yuan per month

988
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,540
and you don't see me complaining.

989
00:35:18,020 --> 00:35:19,340
Talking about money again?

990
00:35:20,130 --> 00:35:21,210
If you want a raise,

991
00:35:21,210 --> 00:35:22,210
just tell me.

992
00:35:24,250 --> 00:35:24,860
Xingfu.

993
00:35:24,860 --> 00:35:25,500
Don't worry.

994
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,340
You just

995
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,500
found us

996
00:35:27,730 --> 00:35:29,250
a huge case.

997
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:31,940
What?

998
00:35:32,210 --> 00:35:33,290
Didn't you just say

999
00:35:33,290 --> 00:35:34,610
it's a small case?

1000
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:38,060
Her case alone

1001
00:35:38,130 --> 00:35:39,250
is a small one.

1002
00:35:39,900 --> 00:35:40,820
But what comes after

1003
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:42,020
is a lot.

1004
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:44,170
If we win this case,

1005
00:35:44,690 --> 00:35:46,730
more farmers will turn to us

1006
00:35:46,860 --> 00:35:47,980
for legal affairs.

1007
00:35:48,690 --> 00:35:49,900
Slowly but surely,

1008
00:35:50,090 --> 00:35:51,290
we'll get the money rolling.

1009
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:52,290
Right.

1010
00:35:53,170 --> 00:35:53,650
Oh.

1011
00:35:54,380 --> 00:35:55,380
Be prepared.

1012
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:57,690
You have a business trip
to Shiqiao Village in a few days.

1013
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,500
What business trip?

1014
00:36:01,250 --> 00:36:02,170
It's just like

1015
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:03,210
what I did with your sister last time.

1016
00:36:03,210 --> 00:36:04,460
We went to your hometown.

1017
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:05,900
We'll go to Shiqiao Village

1018
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:06,940
to understand

1019
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:07,900
the difficulty they face.

1020
00:36:09,090 --> 00:36:10,460
What can I do there?

1021
00:36:10,650 --> 00:36:11,770
A lot.

1022
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:15,940
Okay.

1023
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:16,940
Then

1024
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:18,460
did I make

1025
00:36:18,940 --> 00:36:19,820
a contribution?

1026
00:36:20,210 --> 00:36:21,340
Will I be allowed

1027
00:36:21,340 --> 00:36:22,770
to visit my child on my way back?

1028
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:27,060
What do you say,

1029
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,060
my friends?

1030
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,690
I...

1031
00:36:29,690 --> 00:36:30,340
Stop pretending.

1032
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:31,020
That's a yes.

1033
00:36:33,130 --> 00:36:33,770
Yes.

1034
00:36:35,650 --> 00:36:36,250
Qinglai.

1035
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:39,130
You said Mr. Xu was your uncle

1036
00:36:39,650 --> 00:36:40,900
but he always

1037
00:36:40,900 --> 00:36:42,210
ignores you.

1038
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,650
Are you sure?

1039
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,130
Am I supposed to show you

1040
00:36:45,130 --> 00:36:46,130
how close we are?

1041
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:47,730
My brother keeps pestering me.

1042
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:48,610
Is the favor he asked for

1043
00:36:48,610 --> 00:36:49,690
feasible or not?

1044
00:36:49,690 --> 00:36:50,420
Of course.

1045
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,610
Definitely.

1046
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:55,130
The Provincial Bureau

1047
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:55,980
asked our department

1048
00:36:55,980 --> 00:36:57,460
to do the report this time.

1049
00:36:58,770 --> 00:36:59,940
I had my secretary

1050
00:36:59,940 --> 00:37:01,570
send you the report materials yesterday.

1051
00:37:01,650 --> 00:37:02,380
Have you looked at it?

1052
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:05,210
I have.

1053
00:37:05,770 --> 00:37:06,420
Actually,

1054
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,210
you didn't need to go through me.

1055
00:37:08,770 --> 00:37:09,770
Just report

1056
00:37:09,770 --> 00:37:10,650
the facts.

1057
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:12,610
Right.

1058
00:37:12,690 --> 00:37:13,420
But

1059
00:37:13,980 --> 00:37:15,210
this is a serious matter.

1060
00:37:15,610 --> 00:37:17,060
If I have the support from you, the mayor,

1061
00:37:17,540 --> 00:37:18,610
it'll be safer.

1062
00:37:30,460 --> 00:37:31,060
Uncle.

1063
00:37:31,650 --> 00:37:32,340
Uncle.

1064
00:37:33,290 --> 00:37:34,610
How is Mrs. Xu?

1065
00:37:35,540 --> 00:37:36,340
Lift the bar up.

1066
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:49,090
Are you sure Mr. Xu is your uncle?

1067
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:54,460
Apparently not.

1068
00:37:56,170 --> 00:37:57,610
Once you're an official,

1069
00:37:58,210 --> 00:37:59,380
you become too lofty for your relatives.

1070
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:11,900
[Serve the People]

1071
00:38:14,380 --> 00:38:15,210
Who's that?

1072
00:38:16,770 --> 00:38:17,650
My rela...

1073
00:38:18,650 --> 00:38:20,380
Not even a relative.

1074
00:38:20,380 --> 00:38:20,980
A distant relative

1075
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:22,250
from my hometown,

1076
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:23,500
at most.

1077
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:25,730
You gave him the job?

1078
00:38:26,690 --> 00:38:27,420
Back then,

1079
00:38:27,650 --> 00:38:28,730
several guards complained

1080
00:38:28,980 --> 00:38:30,090
about the low wage

1081
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:31,020
and left.

1082
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,290
We needed people

1083
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,820
so I recommended him to them.

1084
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:34,860
But of course,

1085
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:36,690
the security department decides
if he's up for the job.

1086
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:39,250
Be careful.

1087
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:40,940
Don't make others think

1088
00:38:41,210 --> 00:38:42,170
it's nepotism.

1089
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,650
Thanks for the reminder, Mr. Mayor.

1090
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:45,770
I will take note of it.

1091
00:39:12,730 --> 00:39:13,090
Hey.

1092
00:39:13,210 --> 00:39:13,770
Qingzhi.

1093
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,170
Tonight,

1094
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:17,690
if you're free,

1095
00:39:17,690 --> 00:39:18,860
come visit.

1096
00:39:19,650 --> 00:39:20,650
I need to talk to you.

1097
00:39:22,730 --> 00:39:23,290
Dear.

1098
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:24,210
You're back.

1099
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:26,020
You're off-duty now?

1100
00:39:26,460 --> 00:39:26,980
I have left some dishes for you.

1101
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:27,730
Eat them.

1102
00:39:30,540 --> 00:39:31,860
Why are you packing?

1103
00:39:32,730 --> 00:39:33,340
For a business trip.

1104
00:39:34,570 --> 00:39:35,090
What?

1105
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:36,610
Business trip.

1106
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:37,650
It means the company pays me

1107
00:39:37,730 --> 00:39:38,610
to travel to another place for work.

1108
00:39:38,730 --> 00:39:39,730
It's near our house

1109
00:39:39,730 --> 00:39:40,770
so I can visit Little Dou.

1110
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:43,060
Look at you.

1111
00:39:43,290 --> 00:39:44,340
What can you do?

1112
00:39:45,170 --> 00:39:46,250
To help with a case, of course.

1113
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,090
I helped the law firm

1114
00:39:48,610 --> 00:39:49,940
get a big case.

1115
00:39:50,090 --> 00:39:51,570
Guan Tao asked me to tag along.

1116
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:54,650
Look how happy you are.

1117
00:39:55,570 --> 00:39:56,570
He could be trafficking you

1118
00:39:56,570 --> 00:39:58,020
and you would still be clueless about it.

1119
00:39:58,380 --> 00:39:59,900
I'm not worth a lot anyway.

1120
00:39:59,900 --> 00:40:01,210
Why would someone traffic me?

1121
00:40:03,690 --> 00:40:05,250
You're paid 1,500 yuan per month

1122
00:40:05,250 --> 00:40:06,770
and you have to handle cases too.

1123
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:10,130
I think he's treating you like a slave.

1124
00:40:10,650 --> 00:40:11,500
You're being taken advantage of

1125
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:12,500
and you happily comply.

1126
00:40:13,610 --> 00:40:14,460
Wang Qinglai.

1127
00:40:14,570 --> 00:40:16,130
Why are you so distrustful?

1128
00:40:17,090 --> 00:40:18,610
He thinks highly of me.

1129
00:40:20,250 --> 00:40:21,690
Also, what do I have?

1130
00:40:21,690 --> 00:40:23,610
What do I have to be taken advantage of?

1131
00:40:24,130 --> 00:40:26,060
They like to bully people from rural areas.

1132
00:40:28,090 --> 00:40:29,130
Other than those born in the city,

1133
00:40:29,130 --> 00:40:30,940
even those who came from the rural areas

1134
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:33,060
turn into a different person
once they become rich

1135
00:40:33,690 --> 00:40:34,610
and powerful.

1136
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,460
Who are you talking about?

1137
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,500
Who else could it be?

1138
00:40:43,770 --> 00:40:44,900
Qingzhi's father-in-law.

1139
00:40:46,250 --> 00:40:47,500
He thinks he's all high and mighty.

1140
00:40:48,380 --> 00:40:49,170
He travels around

1141
00:40:49,170 --> 00:40:50,250
but he just ignores me.

1142
00:40:50,900 --> 00:40:51,500
I went to greet him

1143
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:52,250
with a smile

1144
00:40:52,250 --> 00:40:53,340
but he didn't even look at me.

1145
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:55,090
Isn't he just a director?

1146
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:57,290
Back then, I thought he was someone important
in the county.

1147
00:40:57,290 --> 00:40:58,290
But now I know

1148
00:40:58,290 --> 00:40:59,940
that he's no one major in the city.

1149
00:41:02,090 --> 00:41:03,690
You're a security guard.

1150
00:41:03,770 --> 00:41:05,340
Why do you have to approach him?

1151
00:41:06,290 --> 00:41:07,130
I can't?

1152
00:41:08,610 --> 00:41:09,290
Because I'll bring disgrace

1153
00:41:09,290 --> 00:41:10,250
or shame?

1154
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:11,290
In that case,

1155
00:41:11,290 --> 00:41:12,500
just fire me.

1156
00:41:13,460 --> 00:41:14,020
I...

1157
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,130
I wanted to help

1158
00:41:15,130 --> 00:41:16,340
but now, it's a problem.

1159
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:17,570
Sorry,

1160
00:41:17,980 --> 00:41:18,770
Mr. Xu.

1161
00:41:19,860 --> 00:41:20,730
If you think it's inappropriate

1162
00:41:20,730 --> 00:41:22,380
for him to work there,

1163
00:41:22,730 --> 00:41:23,420
I'll find another job

1164
00:41:23,420 --> 00:41:24,690
for him.

1165
00:41:25,090 --> 00:41:26,690
If you could,

1166
00:41:26,770 --> 00:41:28,060
I wouldn't have to help you.

1167
00:41:29,210 --> 00:41:30,570
I just need you

1168
00:41:30,650 --> 00:41:31,820
to tell him

1169
00:41:32,290 --> 00:41:33,380
that he and I

1170
00:41:33,380 --> 00:41:34,460
are two individuals.

1171
00:41:34,540 --> 00:41:36,130
We have no relation whatsoever.

1172
00:41:36,130 --> 00:41:36,650
All right?

1173
00:41:36,650 --> 00:41:37,860
I don't want any trouble.

1174
00:41:38,090 --> 00:41:38,570
Don't worry.

1175
00:41:38,570 --> 00:41:39,570
I'll make it clear to him.

1176
00:41:39,980 --> 00:41:40,650
I'm sure you know

1177
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:42,020
my wife disapproves

1178
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:43,060
of you

1179
00:41:43,570 --> 00:41:45,210
and Yani.

1180
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:48,250
And I have been having your backs.

1181
00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:49,250
You know why?

1182
00:41:50,130 --> 00:41:51,460
Because I believe in you.

1183
00:41:51,460 --> 00:41:52,900
I know you'll be successful.

1184
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:55,570
